==Starting off==
* '''Cook:''' What am I to do? I'm in a terrible mess!
* {{tcond|If the player hasn't completed Cook's Assistant:}}
** {{tmissing}}
* {{tcond|If the player has completed Cook's Assistant:}}
** '''Player:''' This reminds me of how we first met, back in your kitchen in Lumbridge Castle, when you made me fetch the ingredients for a birthday cake.
** '''Cook:''' Yes, this keeps happening to me whenever I cater birthday parties. I just don't have the supplies I need. Can you help?
** {{tselect|Select an Option}}
** {{topt|Why don't you plan better?}}
*** '''Cook:''' I had a plan. It was a great plan.
*** '''Player:''' So...?
*** '''Cook:''' I'd thought the Duke's guests might not come, so I wouldn't have to cater for them.
*** '''Player:''' I see the problem.
*** '''Cook:''' So will you help me?
*** {{topt|Okay, I'll help you.}}
**** {{tact|below}}
*** {{topt|Nope, sort it out yourself.}}
**** {{tact|below}}
** {{topt|Okay, I'll help you.}}
*** '''Player:''' Okay, I'll help you.
*** '''Cook:''' Thank you so much for offering to help me. The Duke told his guests to order whatever they wanted, and they had some odd requests for food and drink. I've written them down in a list...
*** {{tbox|pic=Cook's shopping list detail.png|The Cook gives you a shopping list. You glance over it quickly.}}
*** {{tcond|If the player doesn't have a cabbage on them:}}
**** {{tact|Cook's shopping list interface opens}}
*** {{tcond|If the player has a cabbage on them:}}
**** '''Player:''' I see from the list that you want a cabbage. By a remarkable coincidence, I am already carrying a cabbage.
**** '''Cook:''' Gosh, really? How handy.
**** {{tbox|pic=Cabbage detail.png|You show the Cook the cabbage you got for the Lumbridge Guide.}}
**** '''Cook:''' Thank you, the Lumbridge Guide will be very happy with that.
***** {{tact|end}}
** {{topt|Nope, sort it out yourself.}}
*** {{tmissing}}

===Talking to the Cook again===
* '''Cook:''' How are you getting on with that list?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{tcond|If the player hasn't gotten the letter yet:}}
** {{topt|It says I need a letter from you for a squire.}}
*** '''Player:''' It says I need a letter from you for a squire.
*** '''Cook:''' That's right. Sir Vyvin would never give away his wine, but I think his squire might help us. I'll give you a letter to take to the squire, in Falador Castle.
*** {{tbox|pic=Cook's letter detail.png|The Cook hands you a letter addressed to Sir Vyvin's squire, care of Falador Castle.}}
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{tcond|If the player already gotten the letter:}}
** {{topt|About the letter for the squire...}}
*** {{tcond|If the player lost the letter:}}
**** {{tmissing}}
*** {{tcond|If the player still has a copy of the letter:}}
**** '''Player:''' About the letter for the squire...
**** '''Cook:''' You're meant to be taking it to Sir Vyvin's squire, who's in Falador Castle. Don't tell me you lost it.
**** '''Player:''' No, I have it here.
**** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Have you got another copy of the list?}}
** {{tcond|If the player lost the list:}}
*** {{tmissing}}
** {{tcond|If the player still has a copy of the list:}}
*** '''Player:''' Have you got another copy of the list?
*** '''Cook:''' Oh, have you lost yours?
*** '''Player:''' Nope, I have it with me.
*** '''Cook:''' Then no, I don't have another copy for you.
*** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|I'll keep working on it.}}
** {{tmissing}}

===Talking to the squire===
* {{tcond|Without The Knight's Sword quest completed:}}
* '''Squire:''' Hello. I am the squire to Sir Vyvin.
* {{topt|And how is life as a squire?|event=no}}
* {{topt|A cook gave me a letter for you.}}
** {{tact|below}}
* {{tcond|With The Knight's Sword quest completed:}}
* '''Squire:''' Hello friend! Many thanks for all of your help! Vyvin never even realised it was a different sword, and I still have my job!
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I'm glad the new sword worked out alright.|event=no}}
* {{topt|A cook gave me a letter for you.}}
** '''Player:''' A cook gave me a letter for you.
** '''Squire:''' That's nice. Have you got it?
** {{tbox|pic=Cook's letter detail.png|You show the squire the Cook's letter. He reads it with interest.}}
** '''Squire:''' Gosh, this amazing cook is offering to bake me a birthday cake! I could never afford that sort of thing on my squire allowance.
** '''Player:''' Do be careful, I've seen this cook catering a party before. Also he wants something in return. <!--Maybe Cooks assistant or RFD requirement-->
** '''Squire:''' Yes, he wants some of Sir Vyvin's wine. I shouldn't really do this, but I really would like the birthday cake. Close your eyes for a moment, please...
** {{tact|The squire fetches the wine, ensuring you didn't see where it's stored.}}
** '''Player:''' Thanks!
** {{tact|end}}

===Talking to the Cook after delivering the letter===
* '''Cook:''' How are you getting on with that list?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|I took the letter to the squire.}}
** '''Player:''' I took the letter to the squire.
** '''Cook:''' And he gave you some of Sir Vyvin's wine, which you brought here to me, I remember.
** '''Player:''' Yes, that's what happened.
** {{tact|end}}
* {{topt|Have you got another copy of the list?}}
** {{tact|above}}
* {{topt|I'll keep working on it.}}
** {{tact|above}}

