* '''Barmaid:''' Heya! What can I get you?
* {{tselect|Select an Option}}
* {{topt|What ales are you serving?|event=no}}
* {{topt|cond=If the player has one empty beer glass in their inventory:|I've got this beer glass...|event=no}}
